{
  "contract_version": "lb6-pilot-semantic-abi-v3",
  "task_id": "dev-simple-list",
  "action_schema_markdown": "All arms must implement `reduce(state, action)` accepting these action types:\n\n- `add_item`: payload shape example: `{\"type\":\"add_item\",\"id\":\"item-1\",\"title\":\"Example title\"}`\n- `clear_completed`: payload shape example: `{\"type\":\"clear_completed\"}`\n- `complete_item`: payload shape example: `{\"type\":\"complete_item\",\"id\":\"item-1\"}`\n\n`project(state, actorId)` must return JSON-serializable actor-scoped views used by the behavior grader.\n\nImplementation pressure (honest — not graded substrings):\n- Lifecycle actions must leave distinct inspectable statuses (open vs completed vs overdue/missed with follow-up).\n- Private/sensitive notes must stay distinguishable in the owning actor view.\n- Revoke/expire/deny must change the affected actor projection (access ended / denied), not only UI copy.",
  "projection_contract": {
    "actors": [
      "owner"
    ],
    "shape": "{ items: [{ id, title, completed: boolean, status?: 'open'|'completed' }] }; clear_completed removes completed items and retains open items",
    "typed_equivalents": {
      "complete": [
        true,
        "completed",
        "done"
      ],
      "incomplete": [
        false,
        "open",
        "pending"
      ]
    }
  },
  "scoring_protocol": {
    "behavior_points": 10,
    "raw_score": "earned / 10",
    "valid_reward": "(earned + 1) / 12",
    "determinism": "hard measurement-validity gate"
  },
